{"title":"Vasculitis sistemicas con compromiso de SNC","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Reumatología/Vasculitis sistemicas con compromiso de SNC-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Vasculitis Sistémicas con Compromiso del\\NSistema Nervioso Central (SNC)","guid":"YBAp2Fbo4Y9js_xrRVBN3g","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Caso clínico","guid":"C0iZKQW4D9J0y56KCWjTxg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Información del paciente:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"- Mujer de 28 años con diagnóstico de LES hace 5 años","guid":"UGB9LwCNKGNPwgkAEGsydA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"- Tratamiento actual: Hidroxicloroquina 200 mg/d, Prednisona 5 mg/d","guid":"YJIbnSyo09gR4RTKZTjyng","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Motivo de consulta:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"- Debilidad de extremidad superior derecha de inicio súbito hace 2 días.","guid":"MslwVQTbCyRgmhglYSRYHQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"- Cefalea holocraneal intensa desde hace 1 semana.","guid":"QslAvGQnQbZyhgpELz-Lvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Examen físico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"- PA 140/90 mmHg, FC 88x', T 37. 2°C, FR 18x', Sat 98% AA.","guid":"eb2LPEqgnopt8ms5E31cdQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"- Neurológico:","guid":"QPjB7CfakUsQF1KfTEFbFQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Vigil, orientada. Pares craneales conservados.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"- Fuerza M distal y proximal 3/5 en extremidad superior derecha.","guid":"LZKhHQTi8SlVqi7be257tg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"- Reflejo bicipital y estiloradial derechos disminuidos.","guid":"SUsQkgOmASJrhd0jGauNwg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"- Sensibilidad conservada.","guid":"BDMphTtH5iMqFsA2ZMVFIg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"- Sin signos meníngeos.\\NFondo de ojo normal.","guid":"Z_C5-zv31QFJ_jfAGroqUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"8","text":"- Piel: Eritema malar. Úlceras orales. Livedo reticularis en extremidades inferiores.","guid":"QNLgJSqYT-Z73oJtA5wg4g","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"8","text":"- Cardiopulmonar y abdomen sin hallazgos.","guid":"Dr-RnG5kjLEy26yhCH0c2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"- Hemograma: Hb 11.2, Hto 34%, leucocitos 3200 (RAL 800), plaquetas 112000.","guid":"OQUrOyDOF9sb-nlOef3tKA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"- VHS 62 mm/h, PCR 48 mg/L (VN <5)","guid":"SKipJiwRy-1GP0g9djtKQw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"- C3 52 mg/dL (VN 90-180), C4 6 mg/dL (VN 10-40)","guid":"MPS9FhvpdxlxqcX5ej_NqQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"- Anti-DNA (+). Anticoagulante lúpico (+). Anti-Sm y Anti-RNP (-).","guid":"H494O10voxwT61trI8KhwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"1","text":"- TAC cerebral sin contraste: Normal.","guid":"GHeJPz4CG6EIh-biAGhDOg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"- Vasculitis secundaria a LES con compromiso del SNC.","guid":"efnwolKGHqIbIm2KOszQyA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"- LES con actividad moderada a severa (SLEDAI 15 ptos).","guid":"fR5uiBcA7_c-aPGqC94AJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"1","text":"Manejo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"- Hospitalización.","guid":"BWV8qHFEnksUWxz-Pmqn5A","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"- Metilprednisolona 1 g EV c/24 h por 3 días. Luego prednisona 1 mg/kg/d.","guid":"EhK2JjBVlkw4aJUMWrtfTA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"- Ciclofosfamida 1 g EV c/mes por 6 meses como terapia de inducción.","guid":"XGdiOX6n3UlQ9qmQDVwfTw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"- Anticoagulación con enoxaparina en dosis terapéuticas por presencia de aFL.","guid":"GpFUYkKgb4kHm-z4OiDMnQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"- RNM cerebral con contraste y arteriografía.","guid":"H9ASphuHSGNd425dOEeb5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"1","text":"Seguimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"- RNM muestra lesión isquémica aguda frontal derecha. Arteriografía normal.","guid":"WYlkBWZrVT84r98gU4NUpw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"- Alta al 7° día con leve mejoría de fuerza. Continúa ciclofosfamida ambulatoria.","guid":"OPFz4lPSTKoOUCVvNg_iag","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"- Anticoagulación oral con antagonista de vitamina K. Control de INR.","guid":"atM8oky5FxlB7eKPcDi5Sg","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"- Control con neurología para rehabilitación motora.","guid":"Pf21ZVZI_40uo2EuUBBriw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"- Control reumatología en 1 mes. Planificar terapia de mantención con azatioprina.","guid":"Bp6V2WcL9joqy8rYYwX4Eg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"Gb_ROHZYI2I56CYRfJn2Kg","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"- ¿Qué enfermedad autoinmune se asocia con mayor frecuencia a vasculitis del SNC? R: Lupus eritematoso sistémico (LES). (1)","guid":"eOT4ZVNnv8dgjljMdFFtoQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"- ¿Cuál es la manifestación neurológica más común de la vasculitis 2ª a LES? R: Accidente cerebrovascular (ACV). (1)","guid":"Xrmhaz2taXQ2dlMXMFw1KA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"- ¿Qué anticuerpos se asocian a mayor riesgo de vasculitis del SNC en LES? R: Anticuerpos antifosfolípidos (aFL). (1)","guid":"EuGtRj52OZlJW7tpJvOXDQ","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"- ¿Cómo se manifiesta la vasculitis del SNC en Sjögren? R: Lesiones desmielinizantes multifocales recurrentes. (2)","guid":"LyaK4DBU8NE02VmIe_5Fdw","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"E5lfFFI9v6UwaDuFa0qgzA","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- Vasculitis que afecta vasos sanguíneos del SNC en el contexto de una enfermedad autoinmune sistémica.","guid":"SeKOt00q4GB-eImCJ0Yffg","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"bwCxdxnGqndtb0wOAFLBjA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- Mecanismos (1,2):","guid":"cG6f_lNUlYYEqYhQTyhBaQ","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"- Depósito de complejos inmunes y activación del complemento","guid":"F3MiSR0G4Ddyxjy6EFgarw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"- Daño endotelial mediado por aFL","guid":"EQH--jsf22d_hHaRI-OsQA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"- Infiltración de pared vascular por células inflamatorias","guid":"eZYVAEjgMftK10NNKLyf4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"46","text":"- Objetivos terapéuticos: Suprimir inflamación, prevenir trombosis.","guid":"eTUizH-wnNYkuuVYDM6B4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"Ue5ce1UjIN14GSKtG9DrMw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- Prevalencia de compromiso\\Nneurológico (1, 2):","guid":"Ik4BPXaRrC9DFwqxEU6ytQ","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"- LES: 20-40%","guid":"EFhWpjCGVsARoXRBJ8t47w","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"- Sjögren: 20-25%","guid":"TY029wRnsPs4I5OePfvW9Q","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"- Enfermedad de Behçet: 10-25%","guid":"V7xGgTzNG-4NJBhfaL5Few","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"d-z3VgyojvAMofG7cYMMVg","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"- Enfermedad autoinmune activa o no controlada","guid":"VYjA61d5NQkaP6w3Tr3juA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"- Presencia de aFL, especialmente anticoagulante lúpico (1)","guid":"VynR3z76kY9bjGWYKRguWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"FB2ybFOliEVE6RmNNmuzqQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- LES (1):","guid":"OfX1CV2vOncCmz6UThOndQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- ACV isquémico o hemorrágico","guid":"Sjc0dAgAJD9HumZeWo-LGg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Estado confusional agudo, psicosis, convulsiones (vasculitis vs efecto directo de aFL)","guid":"OIZ6_1lb2p8CWwQKBhOx9g","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"- Corea, mielopatía transversa, meningitis aséptica (menos frecuente)","guid":"XcOLmjp-l6hED4jrNX_SGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"- Sjögren (2):","guid":"EvUd_lIuMkE42PnTCkDRlQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"- Lesiones desmielinizantes multifocales recurrentes (sustancia blanca)","guid":"d0uzl1EzoUoePheWbziq7Q","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"- Mielitis transversa longitudinal extensa","guid":"XdwwOyrgCVJgu7dDM2TxJg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"- Meningoencefalitis, convulsiones","guid":"Alk-W3r7Y3oCItTeWYMQOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"60","text":"- Behçet (3):","guid":"I2HTjFcXEWl5eXyCAT4Dxw","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Lesiones parenquimatosas (tronco-encefálicas, diencefálicas)","guid":"MVTCvEeEWCIEf1sfe4v3MQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"- Trombosis de senos venosos, HTE","guid":"T4R8YUw5wX1WG4JLCAr3YA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"- Meningitis aséptica, mielopatía, neuropatía craneal","guid":"JZWcHVh2hlUOHqlWA1kntw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"K1ukdCJdvfRKFrCuU06kew","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Laboratorio (1):","guid":"b9flbErs_I9FI4o1BEzprw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"- Marcadores de actividad de enfermedad de base (C3, C4, anti-DNA)","guid":"Afcau1o1M8U0ovTtBFBZFg","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"- Perfil de aFL, anticoagulante lúpico","guid":"VTCXQDbFycxd02lQDyaMSQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"- LCR (2): Pleocitosis linfocítica leve, hiperproteinorraquia. Bandas oligoclonales.","guid":"FHUEQ2Bup-VdOjO_RcnG_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"- RNM cerebral (1,2):","guid":"J_MAB2G5jt5BVb4wd3d8aA","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"- Lesiones isquémicas/hemorrágicas","guid":"LfNQWxdxQHx_gnPIU4jseA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"- Hiperintensidades sustancia blanca","guid":"b-fG0Q2hHR5W4hQwAtzkzw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"- Mielitis transversa longitudinal","guid":"X89PXw-7DgMNHbZkAzEi6w","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"- Trombosis senos venosos, realce leptomeníngeo","guid":"ZtIfbAaXMuYEbyayaMk6KA","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"73","text":"- Angiografía (1): Estenosis multisegmentaria, dilataciones aneurismáticas (raro)","guid":"YMxmrDkSG6BtGZM-Nfz97A","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico (1):","guid":"IjuG1Av4XcZSkVYcX6qnkw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"- Clínico + Imágenes compatibles + Enfermedad autoinmune activa","guid":"BBdM0gtsbt9KxiDjMgqdLg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"- Biopsia de SNC generalmente no necesaria","guid":"It2vW0pIlKsFk4mmEsV2LA","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos Diferenciales:","guid":"BKbXAQYgnH1y-fZae2Elhw","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"- Manifestaciones neurológicas no vasculíticas de enfermedad de base","guid":"V-mxyVx1ndYVolr8N7kBKA","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"- Vasculitis primarias del SNC","guid":"bDCr2SLAEWA66iQUUwLLRg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"- Vasculitis infecciosas","guid":"KVdERz9ZSsY7zAVuCiOq8w","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"- Estados protrombóticos no autoinmunes","guid":"eGtmZijlmKxAIKjfaENL0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento (1):","guid":"QAq1RWAE8zpc5srYAXXiVg","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"- Pulsos de metilprednisolona 500-1000 mg/d EV x 3-5 días. Luego prednisona oral.","guid":"c9KVOwVEMxRskDWBHy45rw","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"- Ciclofosfamida en pulsos para inducción. Rituximab como alternativa.","guid":"J6HxCTam5jByfN4qK7k92w","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"- Micofenolato, azatioprina o rituximab para mantención.","guid":"QhNVDz1C_w1dw9sJZPEEag","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"- Anticoagulación/antiagregación si hay aFL.","guid":"B4uTuGNXZLB3tnqWX3VFgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico (1):","guid":"bHZLAxWWSYZYGpRGPrLfeg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"- Mortalidad de 13% a los 5 años en vasculitis 2ª a LES","guid":"P80Chg1Y1ZIXLkaqK_2uYA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"- Recurrencia de 14% a los 7 años con tratamiento","guid":"MBjm81IYar5_AHmmWXArOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"LlrnyD3uNZgDjSmREWGyJw","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"(1) Ramos-Casals M, et al. Vasculitis in systemic lupus erythematosus: prevalence and clinical characteristics in 670 patients. Medicine (Baltimore) 2006; 85:95.","guid":"EXG1hDrMfxRjk9YtCd0b6w","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"(2) Carvajal Alegria G, et al. Epidemiology of neurological manifestations in Sjögren's syndrome. RMD Open 2016; 2:e000179.","guid":"Y7IXwCO0fwxyIGe9V4Ss_A","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"(3) Uygunoğlu U, Siva A. Behçet's Syndrome and Nervous System Involvement. Curr Neurol Neurosci Rep. 2018;18(7):35.","guid":"KPiyIF6wnT92suarUJqjKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"0","text":"Abreviaturas:","guid":"fiA6nUgjysZPnIDeJJL-gA","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"- aFL: Anticuerpos antifosfolípidos","guid":"FVeDb2kvxNZ8U-EFV2rYfg","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"- ACV: Accidente cerebrovascular","guid":"JnLD41oXvA48W9zoLf5XnA","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"- HTE: Hipertensión endocraneana","guid":"QWstESSh48cpOdGlcYQUBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"Vasculitis 2ª a Enfermedades\\NAutoinmunes con Compromiso del SNC","guid":"EVIQFH2sd9Ivl5QocnN7Lg","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"DSjePwjt3XYHO1HKUfBkeg","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"¿Qué vasculitis sistémica se asocia más frecuentemente a compromiso del SNC? R: Vasculitis asociadas a ANCA (AAV), especialmente granulomatosis con poliangeítis (GPA). (1)","guid":"Jf4v-Grr5fNnilUAZL4uAQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"¿Cuáles son las formas más frecuentes de presentación neurológica en AAV? R: Neuropatía craneal (pares craneales), lesiones granulomatosas del SNC, paquimeningitis hipertrófica. (1)","guid":"UWon2gmU-t10LxWMFcX3Og","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"¿Qué vasculitis de grandes vasos puede presentar compromiso neurológico y cómo se manifiesta? R: Arteritis de Takayasu, puede causar ACV por estenosis u oclusión de arterias que derivan del cayado aórtico. (4)","guid":"Cct-vwftyUI9vTBAaDBdnA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"¿Qué vasculitis se asocia a ACV multifocales y deterioro cognitivo subagudo? R: Angeítis primaria del SNC. (5)","guid":"YeIfRVSlPzk1BEIEV_0ojw","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"Lig16hFOYBdkQpQdf5JdxA","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Mecanismos:","guid":"TcEewQ3grwxsW-71LdFImQ","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Inflamación y daño de vasos sanguíneos que irrigan estructuras del SNC → Isquemia y necrosis de parénquima cerebral.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"Infiltración granulomatosa directa en algunas vasculitis (GPA). (1,4)","guid":"ZMmQm1AP62BzIZZ3BUSjZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"114","text":"Sitios afectados:","guid":"WYY2I0M8T_YpxAsXf4RmHA","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Cualquier área del encéfalo y médula espinal.","guid":"GuNa9FhxqakVWFT-JK7Zsw","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Compromiso de pares craneales por extensión de granulomas desde senos paranasales (GPA). (1)","guid":"YF9y7FMVhT4M3zdPQkGSMQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"WP67jj_UjT0UDY9sOV4ueg","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Compromiso del SNC en GPA: 2-8% (1)","guid":"StFWyiF6DIoG1AcxGJJ1iw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Compromiso pares craneales en GPA: 1.5-16% (2)","guid":"L1q7lnMv9idGY74kFCRMMg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"ACV en GPA y PAM: 3-5% (3)","guid":"Qz_hhzmFVJsZaO-WHMYXqw","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Formas de\\Npresentación (1):","guid":"EuoSfCDsxrx7n8CrOqTW9A","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Déficit neurológico focal por ACV isquémico o hemorrágico","guid":"VHtaxACNEeQqfDg_b161uQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Meningitis aséptica y paquimeningitis hipertrófica","guid":"YtBADxXee2tviHmrLaGW2Q","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"Lesiones cerebrales granulomatosas con efecto de masa","guid":"N1iH9XZcgNxGNAxkZrNDjA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Mielopatía transversa","guid":"aYx3AwyXyoh614--LMxYiw","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"Neuropatías craneales","guid":"Rh0fIxRAf1RJknA2Qt7DtQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"126","text":"Mononeuritis múltiple y polineuropatía","guid":"V216AWXc7f1tyJ4wK-jUxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"125","text":"Según la vasculitis (4):","guid":"Zmn_4RhE1nAbR4p-P2i7bw","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Takayasu: ACV (estenosis/oclusión de ramas del arco aórtico), encefalopatía por HTA","guid":"WBljrS9VGet4xunpawN2KQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Angeítis 1ª del SNC: ACV multifocales, deterioro cognitivo subagudo, cefalea, convulsiones","guid":"UEHgp3RmqpQlqE0dMxIgtg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"GPA: Compromiso pares craneales (II, VI, VII), proptosis, masa retroorbitaria, diabetes insípida, convulsiones","guid":"CkUl_xUwxshgs7eQQZ2t9Q","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"EGPA: Mononeuritis múltiple, polineuropatía, ACV","guid":"C41HpSbnw_QoUPGBdRm-qA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"Behçet: Meningoencefalitis, lesiones de tronco, HTE, trombosis de senos venosos","guid":"M3-OfSMogT8h5hczeZytoA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"Cryoglobulinemia: Neuropatía periférica, mononeuritis múltiple, ACV","guid":"N2kAk2t4h2k8e3FVDtZ6lA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"Estudio (4,5):","guid":"e7IL6mML8TQ9Z6zCMxsMfQ","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Laboratorio: Marcadores inflamatorios, ANCA, aFL.","guid":"UVV1ZipED4Y6v09ZN791SA","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"LCR: Pleocitosis a predominio MN, proteinorraquia, cultivos (-). Citología, PCR virus.","guid":"Qojl9lYG2dh3KDC3GqJJow","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"RNM cerebral: Lesiones isquémicas o hemorrágicas, granulomas, realce leptomeníngeo.","guid":"BVvzw2_vGqEFpb_NVZ3Uag","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"Angio-RNM o angio-TAC: Estenosis multisegmentaria, oclusión vascular, microaneurismas.","guid":"ZFXFNStODOoIr_UgbprrNQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"Arteriografía cerebral: Gold standard para compromiso de vasos intracraneales.","guid":"QH7Ts2ljrLAwOJkqTAwbWA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"140","text":"Biopsia cerebral, leptomenínges o arteria temporal: Vasculitis, infiltrado granulomatoso.","guid":"EEtwpViJiqtBJdoAQ8r_Ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico (5):","guid":"ToR4nXnjHhhB8YcRH9nuBA","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"Angeítis primaria del SNC:","guid":"JCctnnyw1mpXmWNMZrATlA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Clínica + Arteriografía con estenosis multiseg